   Demi, 27, stunned her 19.9 million Instagram followers as she shared her reel entitled: “Boat Day: Mykonos”. The star looked like she was having the time of her life, as she included shots of herself enjoying drinks with pals, posing for photoshoots and lounging on the beach. “Feelin’ nauti” she captioned the sizzling snaps, which displayed several cleavage-baring outfits. (sic) The model could be seen rocking a bejewelled bikini, a plunging red gown and going topless in some tiny pants.  